    "notes": "Aranese (Gascon Occitan) accentuation per the Conselh Generau dAran norm: same default-final, vowel/vowel+s → paroxytone rule as standard Occitan; written accents override. Aranese ⟨a⟩ in stressed position is typically [a] (not [ɔ] as standard Oc). Pattern inherited from Gascon prosody."
